description:
The talented team behind Toronto Comics: Volume 2 are back with fresh stories set in your neighbourhood!

These four all-new comics, exclusively in this collection, are a bonus for longtime fans and a sample for new readers of what Toronto Comics has to offer.
name: Vol. 1

description:
In the near future, a small team of genetically engineered meta-humans defend our country's interests at home and abroad...

They are the Vanguard.

It is the not too distant future. Our world is has become more politically and economically unstable. Food riots, water and power shortages and a rising crime rate make day to day living a constant struggle.

What starts as a simple rescue mission reveals a new, terrifying threat - An unseen enemy, with a vast array of terrible weapons and access to seemingly unlimited resources. Can our heroes uncover who they are and stop their diabolical machinations before the world is plunged in to chaos?

This 160+ page book collects the complete issues 1-5 of the webcomic Vanguard, previously published on VanguardComic.com and includes unseen and unpublished designs and artwork!
name: Book One

description: What you think you know about unicorns is a lie. A lie woven into the very fabric of our history and perpetuated by an evil, ageless conspiracy. This is the untold story of a ragtag band of Vikings hellbent on revenge and sworn to stave off an invasion of monstrous proportions.

He has been Sent to Their World in order to Save his Own

Rowen of Cadabra has been charged with a delicate mission: Stop the goblins before they enter his forest. But in order to do that, he must leave behind his world of magic and danger and enter the strange world of civilization. Fitting in with the ho-hum locals during the day, and combating seven deadly goblins by night keeps Rowen plenty busy.

In this premier issue, a catastrophe causes the sleepy Cadabrans to finally take action upon those who would do them harm. Or rather, they assign the task to their most socially outcasted member. After finding out the details of his quest, Rowen sets off for the haunted tower, and meets the ice demoness who dwells inside.
name: Book 1

description: Join the Goats are they begin the rise against the human race, going from one of the most beloved farm animals, to demonic bringers of death!
Doing research for a new project, Max meets up with Isabelle, Leah, and Cassie for the first time. Hi-jinks and hilarity ensue.

The Multiverse

Who is Zetaman? Why is such a depressing real life superhero important? And what is the Multiverse? Find out in Zetaman: The Multiverse.
name: The Multiverse
